the soviet union is standing together with the 
united states and other western governments in the persian gulf 
crisis but things could have been different 
what if mikhail s gorbachev had not become president and 
introduced political and economic reforms how would former soviet 
leaders who sent tanks into czechoslovakia and troops into 
afghanistan have reacted to the actions of iraqi president saddam 
hussein 
