security police in a hall off the conference site 
a security official named felipe zilla intimated to cox that 
mr restano was in danger the league said and expressed concern 
that the cubans threatened and followed by security officials 
may suffer reprisals now that the conference ended 
the week long congress held by the un every five years aims 
at formulating guidelines on fighting crime while protecting 
prisoners from abuse and their lawyers from reprisals in countries 
under authoritarian governments 
