produced by about five different companies he said there was no 
way to tell which companys product caused the infection if any 
or if it may have been caused by whole blood they received 
during the litigation cutter laboratories mistakenly gave the 
rays attorneys a memo showing that cutters own attorney 
recommended as early as 1982 that plasma products carry warnings 
about aids cutter and armour didnt begin including the warnings 
until 1984 
