weaken and the same course was expected for the next 24 hours 
isidore reached hurricane strength late thursday only a day 
after it had formed into the ninth named storm of the 1990 atlantic 
hurricane season 
a hurricane has sustained winds of at least 74 mph while 
tropical storms have a threshold of 39 mph 
