bread shortages have spread from moscow to other 
cities including leningrad and soldiers have been mobilized to 
help bakers in the capital soviet media reported saturday 
there is a terrible shortage of flour and yeast the head of 
leningrads central baking plants told pravda the communist party 
newspaper 
