darkman is just a comic book character but we did try to show 
him as a man who wanted to be loved and wanted to be accepted 
because of his growing alienation and frustration dealing with 
rejection by the woman who loves him the fact he continously 
failed thats why he becomes a bad character as opposed to just 
the way he looks 
who is sam raimi hes a native of royal oak mich who began 
making films at age 11 and collecting comic books much sooner he 
has thousands of them outside of the three stooges and jerry 
lewis he didnt watch movies as a kid so darkman is not 
simply a takeoff on horror films but also a personal statement 
about beauty and selfesteem 
all men at times think theyre the ugly ones he said 
maybe theyre rejected because theyre so hideous im sure ive 
been in a role like the darkman you consider yourself ugly and are 
frustrated with your failure and feel low about yourself 
i understand the loneliness aspect and rejection aspect 
after graduating from high school he planned on studying film 
