gags together making darkman a comic phantom story that pumps 
a little life into biff bam and pow 
comic books approach each frame that mostly clearly depicts 
the action and is their most dramatic representation of the action 
i took a similar appraoch when i directed darkman even at the 
cost of losing reality or drama or melodrama he said 
